'White is lost without counterplay, since the black forces are completely
controlling the chessboard.'} 34. Qf1 Bxf4 $19 35. Nc7 Qd2 36. Ne8+ Nxe8 37.
Rxe8 Qe3 38. Bf3 Bxf3 39. gxf3 Qd2 40. Qg1 Qe2 {Ftacnik: 'After the win of the
fourth pawn Mamedyarov would easily win any endgame.'} 0-1

